text: "Run" is a 2002 song by the German DJ group Sash! and it features English singer Boy George. It is the second single from Sash's fourth studio album S4!Sash! which was released on 24 June 2002. ==Charts== Chart (2002) Peak position ==References== Category:2002 songs Category:Eurodance songs Category:Sash! songs
